{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/push-elements-left-or-right-with-the-float-property","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"applied-visual-design","demoType":null,"title":"Pomerite elemente levo ili desno koristeci float svojstvo","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Sledeca tehnika za raspored ne koristi <code>position</code>, vec postavlja <code>float</code> svojstvo elementa. Elementi koji su float-ovani uklanjaju se iz normalnog toka dokumenta i pomeraju na <code>left</code> ili <code>right</code> stranu roditeljskog elementa koji ih sadrzi. Ovo se cesto koristi zajedno sa <code>width</code> svojstvom da bi se definisalo koliko horizontalnog prostora je elementu potrebno.</p>\n</section>","id":"587d78a3367417b2b2512ace","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Dati markup bi bolje radio kao raspored u dve kolone, gde su <code>section</code> i <code>aside</code> elementi jedan pored drugog. Dodelite elementu <code>#left</code> <code>float</code> svojstvo sa vrednoscu <code>left</code>, a elementu <code>#right</code> <code>float</code> svojstvo sa vrednoscu <code>right</code>.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/c/c2MDqu2","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301066,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/push-elements-left-or-right-with-the-float-property"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<head>\n  <style>\n    #left {\n\n      width: 50%;\n    }\n    #right {\n\n      width: 40%;\n    }\n    aside, section {\n      padding: 2px;\n      background-color: #ccc;\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <header>\n    <h1>Welcome!</h1>\n  </header>\n  <section id=\"left\">\n    <h2>Content</h2>\n    <p>Good stuff</p>\n  </section>\n  <aside id=\"right\">\n    <h2>Sidebar</h2>\n    <p>Links</p>\n  </aside>\n</body>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Element sa id vrednoscu <code>left</code> treba da ima <code>float</code> vrednost <code>left</code>.</p>","testString":"const leftElement = document.querySelector('#left');\nconst leftStyle = window.getComputedStyle(leftElement);\nassert.equal(leftStyle?.float, 'left');"},{"text":"<p>Element sa id vrednoscu <code>right</code> treba da ima <code>float</code> vrednost <code>right</code>.</p>","testString":"const rightElement = document.querySelector('#right');\nconst rightStyle = window.getComputedStyle(rightElement);\nassert.equal(rightStyle?.float, 'right');"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/#applied-visual-design","dashedName":"push-elements-left-or-right-with-the-float-property","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"applied-visual-design","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/change-the-position-of-overlapping-elements-with-the-z-index-property","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/lock-an-element-to-the-browser-window-with-fixed-positioning","id":"587d78a3367417b2b2512ace","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<style>\n  .balls {\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    position: fixed;\n    width: 50px;\n    height: 50px;\n    top: 60%;\n    animation-name: jump;\n    animation-duration: 2s;\n    animation-iteration-count: infinite;\n  }\n  #red {\n    background: red;\n    left: 25%;\n    animation-timing-function: linear;\n  }\n  #blue {\n    background: blue;\n    left: 50%;\n    animation-timing-function: ease-out;\n  }\n  #green {\n    background: green;\n    left: 75%;\n    animation-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.311, 0.441, 0.444, 1.649);\n  }\n\n  @keyframes jump {\n    50% {\n      top: 10%;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n<div class=\"balls\" id=\"red\"></div>\n<div class=\"balls\" id=\"blue\"></div>\n<div class=\"balls\" id=\"green\"></div>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/push-elements-left-or-right-with-the-float-property"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}